article_title: Tenet Healthcare Swings to Profit on Higher Admissions
article_text:
Tenet Healthcare Corp. swung to a profit in the fourth quarter, as the hospital operator recorded higher admissions and revenue.

The company, which in recent quarters had seen improved results from the U.S. health-care policy overhaul as newly insured patients sought treatment, attributed most of its admissions growth in the fourth quarter to...
